<?php
return ['messages'=>['<p><span class="trx_addons_dark" style="font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-style: normal;"><strong>May 30-June 3, 2024</strong></span></p><p><strong>BOOTH </strong>#63309</p><p class="last-child"><strong>VENUE </strong>The Venetian Hotel</p>'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_dark" style="font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-style: normal;"><strong>2024 年 5 月 30 日至 6 月 3 日</strong></span></p><p><strong>展位 </strong>#63309</p><p class="last-child"><strong>場地 </strong>The Venetian Hotel（威尼斯人酒店）</p>','<p><span class="trx_addons_dark"><strong>June 20-23, 2024</strong></span></p><p><strong>BOOTH </strong>#1C302</p><p class="last-child"><strong>VENUE </strong>Hong Kong Convention and Exhibition Centre</p>'=>'<p><span class="trx_addons_dark"><strong>2024 年 6 月 20 日至 23 日</strong></span></p><p><strong>展位 </strong>#1C302</p><p class="last-child"><strong>場地 </strong>香港會議展覽中心</p>','<p><strong><big>Follow us</big></strong></p>'=>'<p><strong><big>關注我們</big></strong></p>','<p><strong><span class="trx_addons_dark">September 18-22, 2024</span></strong></p><p><strong>BOOTH</strong> #1C302</p><p><strong>VENUE</strong> Hong Kong Convention and Exhibition Centre</p>'=>'<p><strong><span class="trx_addons_dark">2024 年 9 月 18 日至 22 日</span></strong></p><p><strong>展位</strong> #1C302</p><p><strong>場地</strong> 香港會議展覽中心</p>','<p><strong><span class="trx_addons_dark">September 6-10, 2024</span></strong></p><p><strong>BOOTH</strong> Hall 3.1 B113-114</p><p><strong>VENUE</strong> Fiera di Vicenza</p>'=>'<p><strong><span class="trx_addons_dark">2024 年 9 月 6 日至 10 日</span></strong></p><p><strong>攤位</strong> 3.1 號館 B113-114</p><p><strong>場地</strong> 維琴察展覽中心</p>','<p>As always, we have been continually delighted by your presence at each milestone, your eyes reflecting the gleam of our exquisite jewellery creations, and your support fueling our passion for excellence.</p><p>Now, with eyes set on the horizon, we warmly invite you to join us to continue this journey with us. We look forward to welcoming you to <a href="https://eji.com.hk/portfolio/jck-las-vegas-2024/">JCK Las Vegas</a> and seeing you again at the <a href="https://eji.com.hk/portfolio/jewellery-gem-fair-asia-2024/">Jewellery &amp; Gem Fair Asia</a> in Hong Kong. Creative and sophisticated jewellery pieces promise to be the bright sparks in our upcoming collections ahead.</p><p>Until then, may we consistently astonish and enchant you with our bespoke fine jewellery service - more spotlights of imagination are yet to ignite!</p>'=>'<p>一如既往，我們一直很高興您的光臨每一個里程碑，您的眼睛映照著我們精美珠寶作品的光芒，您的支援激發了我們追求卓越的熱情。</p><p>現在，我們放眼未來，熱忱邀請您加入我們，與我們一起繼續這段旅程。我們期待著歡迎您來到 <a href="https://eji.com.hk/portfolio/jck-las-vegas-2024/">JCK Las Vegas</a> ，並再次在香港的 <a href="https://eji.com.hk/portfolio/jewellery-gem-fair-asia-2024/">亞洲珠寶和寶石博覽會</a> 上見到您。富有創意和精緻的珠寶作品有望成為我們即將推出的系列中的璀璨火花。  </p><p>在那之前，願我們始終如一地以我們的定製高級珠寶服務讓您感到驚訝和陶醉 - 更多想像力的聚光燈尚未點燃！</p>','<p>As the first quarter drew to a close, we presented our jewellery creations at the world-class <a href="https://www.hktdc.com/event/hkjewellery/en">Hong Kong International Jewellery Show</a>. This enchanting stage highlighted our latest fine jewellery pieces – each a testament to meticulous craftsmanship and attention to detail, capturing the spirit of contemporary design with a touch of timeless elegance.</p>'=>'<p>隨著第一季度接近尾聲，我們在世界級的 <a href="https://www.hktdc.com/event/hkjewellery/tc">香港國際珠寶展</a>上展示了我們的珠寶作品。這個迷人的舞臺突出了我們最新的高級珠寶作品——每一件作品都證明瞭一絲不苟的工藝和對細節的關注，以永恆的優雅捕捉現代設計的精神。 </p>','<p>As the new year sparkled with promise of <em>creativity and adventure</em>, our first three months dazzled on the global stage with a sequence of enlightening exhibitions across the world. With a line-up of engaging exhibitions, we have eagerly presented our diverse range of new collections, embarking on our enriching journey through the realm of the fine jewellery.</p>'=>'<p>隨著新的一年充滿 <em>創造力和冒險</em>的光芒，我們的前三個月在全球舞臺上熠熠生輝，在世界各地舉辦了一系列富有啟發性的展覽。通過一系列引人入勝的展覽，我們熱切地展示了我們多樣化的新系列，踏上了我們在高級珠寶領域的豐富旅程。 </p>','<p>In February, our path led us to Sharjah in the Middle East, where the prestigious <a href="https://www.mideastjewellery.com/">Watch and Jewellery Middle East Show</a> was held. This beacon of luxury exhibited the most extensive and exclusive fine jewellers from across the world, showcasing our jewellery pieces ranging from classy elegance to maximalist splendor, captivating the creative spirit and imagination of all.</p>'=>'<p>2 月，我們前往中東的沙迦，在那裡舉行了著名的 <a href="https://www.mideastjewellery.com/">Watch and Jewellery Middle East Show</a> 。這個奢華的燈塔展示了來自世界各地的最廣泛和最獨特的高級珠寶商，展示了我們的珠寶作品，從優雅到極繁華，吸引了所有人的創造精神和想像力。 </p>','<p>Kicking off in January, we set a glittering commencement of the year at <a href="https://www.vicenzaoro.com/en/">VicenzaOro January Edition</a>, where we basked in the debut of jewellery pieces embodying a vision of elegance and unwavering dedication in this historic city of Italy.</p>'=>'<p>從 1 月開始，我們在 <a href="https://www.vicenzaoro.com/en/">VicenzaOro January Edition</a> 上為新的一年設定了一個閃閃發光的開端，在那裡我們沉浸在珠寶作品的首次亮相中，這些珠寶作品體現了這座義大利歷史名城的優雅願景和堅定不移的奉獻精神。</p>','<p>Our journey continued and Germany then called our talents. <a href="https://inhorgenta.com/en/">Inhorgenta</a> in Munich welcomed us to join to exhibit in their Fine Jewellery Hall. Here, we embodied our commitment in elegance, innovation and sustainability. Our booth, crafted from sustainable oak, became a nexus for connecting with jewellery elites worldwide who share our vision, reinforcing our distinguished image within the fine jewellery industry.</p>'=>'<p>我們的旅程繼續，然後德國召喚了我們的人才。慕尼克的 <a href="https://inhorgenta.com/en/">Inhorgenta</a> 歡迎我們加入他們的高級珠寶館展出。在這裡，我們體現了我們對優雅、創新和可持續發展的承諾。我們的展位採用可持續橡木製成，成為與世界各地擁有相同願景的珠寶精英建立聯繫的紐帶，鞏固了我們在高級珠寶行業的獨特形象。  </p>','Connect with us'=>'與我們聯繫','JCK Las Vegas'=>'JCK 拉斯維加斯','Jewellery & Gem Fair ASIA'=>'亞洲珠寶與寶石展','Jewellery & Gem Fair WORLD'=>'珠寶與寶石博覽會 WORLD','VicenzaOro Sep'=>'維琴察奧羅 9 月','editor-text-edit